<exercise id="fs-id1167661293921">
<problem id="fs-id1167663661514">
<para id="fs-id1167663661517">Coombs’ reagent is an antiserum with antibodies that bind to human ________.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167663987309">
<para id="fs-id1167663987311">immunoglobulins/antibodies and/or complement</para>
</solution>
